Philadelphia's Magic Gardens on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/philadelphias-magic-gardens/img-1100-23.jpg\" alt=\"Philadelphia's Magic Gardens on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/philadelphias-magic-gardens/img-0608-24.jpg\" alt=\"Philadelphia's Magic Gardens on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/philadelphias-magic-gardens/img-0607-25.jpg\" alt=\"Philadelphia's Magic Gardens on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5558 post__image\" src=\"/posts/philadelphias-magic-gardens/img-0619-e1428356475821-26.jpg\" alt=\"Philadelphia's Magic Gardens on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"960\" height=\"1280\"></p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/philadelphias-magic-gardens/img-0540-27.jpg\" alt=\"Philadelphia's Magic Gardens on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/philadelphias-magic-gardens/img-0536-28.jpg\" alt=\"Philadelphia's Magic Gardens on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/philadelphias-magic-gardens/img-0607-25.jpg\" alt=\"Philadelphia's Magic Gardens on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/philadelphias-magic-gardens/img-0529-29.jpg\" alt=\"Philadelphia's Magic Gardens on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5554 post__image\" src=\"/posts/philadelphias-magic-gardens/img-0546-30.jpg\" alt=\"Philadelphia's Magic Gardens on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"960\" height=\"1280\"></p>\n<p>The mosaic archway that says “Picture” with the fully mosaic’d wall behind it is probably my favorite pic, though they are all amazing. And these photos are only a small fraction of what is there! I can’t wait to go back, and bring some friends and family with me next time!</p>\n<p>Have you ever been to the Philly Magic Gardens?</p>\n",
